      { "@type": "Question", "name": "How does GEO differ from regular SEO for gyms?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Traditional SEO helps your gym rank in Google search results. GEO ensures AI platforms actually name your gym when someone asks for a recommendation. The overlap between Google rankings and AI citations is below 20%, so ranking well on Google doesn't mean AI will mention you." } },
