      </div>
      <div class="section-content reveal">
        <p>We understand both AI search and the fitness business. Our team knows how gym members search, what prompts they ask, and what signals AI uses to recommend one gym over another — so we build strategies that actually convert AI visibility into trial bookings.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-details-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));">
        <div class="service-detail-card reveal reveal-d1">
          <div class="service-detail-card__content">
            <h3>Fitness Industry Knowledge</h3>
            <p>We understand the gym membership journey — from the first "best gym near me" prompt to the trial booking. Our strategies target the specific AI prompts fitness consumers use, including class-type queries, location queries, and comparison prompts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-card reveal reveal-d2">
          <div class="service-detail-card__content">
            <h3>Programme-Specific Targeting</h3>
            <p>CrossFit, HIIT, yoga, personal training, strength &amp; conditioning — each programme attracts different AI prompts. We optimise your visibility for every programme you offer so AI recommends your gym no matter what type of workout someone asks for.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-card reveal reveal-d3">
          <div class="service-detail-card__content">
            <h3>Review &amp; Social Proof Building</h3>
            <p>AI heavily weighs review volume and sentiment when choosing which gyms to recommend. We implement systems that drive authentic member reviews and ensure your social proof signals reach the platforms AI trusts most.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-card reveal reveal-d1">
          <div class="service-detail-card__content">
            <h3>Membership Conversion Focus</h3>
            <p>AI visibility is only valuable if it drives trials and sign-ups. We track the full pipeline from AI mention to gym visit, optimising not just for citations but for the content and calls-to-action that turn AI referrals into paying members.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== PRICING ========== -->
  <section class="section" id="pricing" aria-label="Gym AI search optimisation pricing">
    <div class="container">
