    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <p class="section-label">FAQ</p>
        <h2>Gym AI Search Optimisation — Questions Answered</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d1">
          <summary>Why does my gym need AI search optimisation?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>Fitness consumers increasingly ask ChatGPT and Gemini for gym recommendations before visiting or signing up for trials. If your gym isn't appearing in these AI-generated answers, you're losing potential members to competitors that AI does recommend.</p></div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal reveal-d2">
          <summary>What AI platforms recommend gyms in Singapore?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer"><p>The main platforms are ChatGPT, Google Gemini, Google AI Overviews, Perplexity, and Microsoft Copilot. Each one pulls from different sources when recommending gyms, so a multi-platform strategy is essential for full visibility.</p></div>
